==Awards and nominations==
{{main|List of awards and nominations received by Chely Wright}}

Wright has received several awards and nominations for her work. This includes one win the [[Academy of Country Music Awards]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Search winners: Chely Wright |url=https://www.acmcountry.com/winners?awardTitle=chely+wright&awardCategory=&awardYear=&actionButton=Submit |website=[[Academy of Country Music Awards]] |access-date=February 5, 2021}}</ref> three nominations from the [[Country Music Association Awards]],<ref>{{cite web |title=CMA Awards Past Winners & Nominees |url=https://cmaawards.com/past-winners-and-nominees/?appSession=33GJN1J1HH2KTG3NO4GPP0GB198E3GK4779652ALGGA7C78X1D498BLSY65127NZI741Q106IMRO0OS7E6D5M6FR919724IXZ47ES8K8VP8VHN52B267WN902L04FXA3 |website=[[Country Music Association]] |access-date=February 5, 2021}}</ref> and two nominations from [[GLAAD]].<ref>{{cite web |title=GLAAD Media Awards Nominees |url=https://www.glaad.org/mediaawards/22/nominees |website=[[GLAAD Media Award]]s |date=September 9, 2011 |access-date=February 5, 2021}}</ref><ref name="glaad.org"/>

==Books==
